hestra La Scintilla]] / [[\u00c1d\u00e1m Fischer]] (Decca)\n*Instrumental (Record of the Year) &ndash; [[Beethoven]], ''Piano Sonatas, Vol 4'' [[Paul Lewis (pianist)|Paul Lewis]] ([[Harmonia Mundi]])\n*Baroque Vocal &ndash; [[Monteverdi]], ''[[L'Orfeo]]'', [[La Venexiana]] / [[Claudio Cavina]] (Glossa)\n*Choral &ndash; [[Haydn]], ''[[The Creation (Haydn)|The Creation]]'', Soloists, Gabrieli Consort and Players / [[Paul McCreesh]] ([[Archiv Produktion]])\n*Contemporary &ndash; [[Jonathan Harvey (composer)|Jonathan Harvey]], Body Mandala, Anu Komsi, [[BBC Scottish Symphony Orchestra]] / [[Ilan Volkov]] (NMC)\n*Early Music &ndash; [[Nicholas Ludford]], Missa Benedicta, Choir of New College, Oxford / Edward Higginbottom (K617)\n*Historic Reissue \u2013 [[Sibelius]], ''Songs'', [[Kim Borg]], [[Erik Werba]] ([[Deutsche Grammophon]])\n*Orchestral &ndash; [[Myaskovsky]], ''Symphonies'', USSR State & Russian Federation Symphony Orchestras / [[Evgeny Svetlanov]] (Warner Classics)\n*Solo vocal &ndash; [[Samuel Barber|Barber]], ''Songs'', [[Gerald Finley]], [[Julius Drake]], ([[Hyperion Records|Hyperion]])\n*Editor's Choice &ndash; ''Mr Abel's Fine Airs''\n\n===2007===\n*Artist of the Year &ndash; [[Julia Fischer]]\n*Lifetime Achievement &ndash; [[Montserrat Caball\u00e9]]\n*Young Artist of the Year &ndash; [[Vasily Petrenko]]\n*Special Achievement &ndash; Christopher Raeburn\n*Label of the Year &ndash; [[Deutsche Grammophon]]\n*Concerto (Record of the Year) &ndash; [[Johannes Brahms|Brahms]] Piano Concertos [[Nelson Freire]]; Leipzig Gewandaus Orchestra / Riccardo Chailly (Decca)\n*Editor's Choice &ndash; [[Gustav Mahler|Mahler]] [[Symphony No. 2 (Mahler)|Symphony No. 2]] [[Budapest Festival Orchestra]] / [[Ivan Fischer]] ([[Channel Classics Records|Channel Classics]])\n*Baroque instrumental &ndash; [[George Frideric Handel|Handel]] Concerti Grossi Academy of Ancient Music / [[Richard Egarr]] (Harmonia Mundi)\n*Baroque vocal &ndash; [[George Frideric Handel|Handel]] [[Messiah 