zay]] (baritone), Jacqueline Bonneau (piano), Orchestre de la Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 des Concerts du Conservatoire / Edouard Lindenberg (Testament)\n*Orchestral &ndash; [[Arnold Bax]] ''The Symphonies'', [[BBC Philharmonic Orchestra]] / Vernon Handley ([[Chandos Records|Chandos]])\n\n===2003===\n*Artist of the Year &ndash; [[Marin Alsop]]\n*Lifetime Achievement Award &ndash; [[Leontyne Price]]\n*Special Achievement Award &ndash; [[Vernon Handley]]\n*Label of the Year &ndash; [[Harmonia Mundi]]\n*Chamber Music (Record of the Year) &ndash; [[Robert Schumann|Schumann]] ''String Quartets Nos 1 & 3'' \u2013 Zehetmair Quartet, ECM\n*Classic FM Listener's Choice &ndash; [[Cecilia Bartoli]]\n*D\u00e9but Disc and Editor's Choice &ndash; Prokofiev; Scriabin; Stravinsky; Tchaikovsky Piano Works, [[Simon Trpceski]]\n*Baroque Vocal &ndash; Handel: Arcadian Duets. Emmanuelle Ha\u00efm, Le Concert d'Astr\u00e9e. Virgin Classics.\n*Choral &ndash; [[Johann Nepomuk Hummel]], Masses, [[Collegium Musicum 90]], [[Richard Hickox]] ([[Chandos Records]])\n*Orchestral &ndash; Sibelius: Rondo of the waves; Lahti SO, Osmo V\u00e4nsk\u00e4 (BIS)\n*Concerto &ndash; [[Antonio Vivaldi]], Violin Concertos, Op 4, ''La Stravaganza'', Arte dei Suonatori, [[Rachel Podger]] [[Channel Classics Records|Channel Classics]] CCS19598)\n*Contemporary &ndash; Steve Reich: City Life. Ensemble Modern. RCA.\n*Early Music &ndash; The Call of the Phoenix: Rare 15th-century English Church Music. The Orlando Consort. Harmonia Mundi.\n*Instrumental &ndash; [[Chopin]], Etudes, Opp 10 & 12, [[Murray Perahia]] (Sony Classical SK61885)\n*Opera &ndash; [[Benjamin Britten]], [[The Turn of the Screw (opera)|The Turn of the Screw]], [[Ian Bostridge]], [[Mahler Chamber Orchestra]], [[Daniel Harding]] ([[Virgin Records|Virgin Classics]])\n\n===2002===\n*Artist of the Year &ndash; [[Maxim Vengerov]]\n*Lifetime Achievement &ndash; [[Mirella Freni]]\n*Concerto (Record of the Year) &ndash; [[Camille Saint-Sa\u00ebns|Saint-Sa\u00ebns]], 