ongs'', [[Gerald Finley]], [[Julius Drake]], ([[Hyperion Records|Hyperion]])\n*Editor's Choice &ndash; ''Mr Abel's Fine Airs''\n\n===2007===\n*Artist of the Year &ndash; [[Julia Fischer]]\n*Lifetime Achievement &ndash; [[Montserrat Caball\u00e9]]\n*Young Artist of the Year &ndash; [[Vasily Petrenko]]\n*Special Achievement &ndash; Christopher Raeburn\n*Label of the Year &ndash; [[Deutsche Grammophon]]\n*Concerto (Record of the Year) &ndash; [[Johannes Brahms|Brahms]] Piano Concertos [[Nelson Freire]]; Leipzig Gewandaus Orchestra / Riccardo Chailly (Decca)\n*Editor's Choice &ndash; [[Gustav Mahler|Mahler]] [[Symphony No. 2 (Mahler)|Symphony No. 2]] [[Budapest Festival Orchestra]] / [[Ivan Fischer]] ([[Channel Classics Records|Channel Classics]])\n*Baroque instrumental &ndash; [[George Frideric Handel|Handel]] Concerti Grossi Academy of Ancient Music / [[Richard Egarr]] (Harmonia Mundi)\n*Baroque vocal &ndash; [[George Frideric Handel|Handel]] [[Messiah (Handel)|Messiah]] (Dublin version, 1742); Dunedin Consort & Players / John Butt (Linn Records)\n*Chamber &ndash; Haas and Jan\u00e1\u010dek String Quartets Pavel Haas Quartet (Supraphon)\n*Choral &ndash; [[Johannes Brahms|Brahms]] [[Ein Deutsches Requiem]] Dorothea R\u00f6schmann; [[Thomas Quasthoff]]; Berlin Radio Choir; [[Berlin Philharmonic Orchestra]] / [[Sir Simon Rattle]] (EMI)\n*Contemporary &ndash; Julian Anderson Alhambra Fantasy [[BBC Symphony Orchestra]] / [[Oliver Knussen]] ([[Ondine (record label)|Ondine]])\n*DVD &ndash; Julian Bream: My Life in Music(Avie)\n*Early music &ndash; [[William Byrd|Byrd]] Laudibus in sanctis [[The Cardinall's Musick]] / [[Andrew Carwood]] (Hyperion)\n*Historic reissue &ndash; [[Symphony in G minor (Moeran)|Moeran Symphony in G minor]] etc. [[London Philharmonic Orchestra]], New Philharmonia / [[Sir Adrian Boult]] (Lyrita)\n*History archive &ndash; [[Richard Wagner|Wagner]] [[G\u00f6tterd\u00e4mmerung]] Bayreuth Festival Opera / [[Joseph Keilberth]] (Testament)\n*Instrumental &n